<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Erreur de connexion MoneyPitch - ADN Family Office</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="{{ asset('assets/favicon.svg') }}" type="image/svg+xml">
    <link rel="icon" href="{{ asset('assets/favicon.ico') }}" sizes="any">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --adn-primary: #1C29A1;
            --adn-primary-light: #3B82F6;
            --adn-error: #EF4444;
            --adn-error-dark: #DC2626;
            --adn-warning: #F59E0B;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F1751 0%, #1C29A1 30%, #2D3FDB 70%, #3B82F6 100%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .logo {
            height: 45px;
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        /* Container principal */
        .main-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        /* Card d'erreur */
        .error-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            max-width: 480px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 
                0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            animation: slideUp 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Icône d'erreur */
        .error-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--adn-error) 0%, var(--adn-error-dark) 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
        }

        .error-icon svg {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Titre */
        .error-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--adn-error);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        /* Message d'erreur */
        .error-message-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FEF2F2 0%, #FEE2E2 100%);
            border: 1px solid #FECACA;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--adn-error);
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .error-message-box p {
            color: #991B1B;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Info box */
        .info-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFFBEB 0%, #FEF3C7 100%);
            border: 1px solid #FDE68A;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--adn-warning);
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .info-box-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #92400E;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .info-box p {
            color: #92400E;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Code erreur */
        .error-code {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            background: #F3F4F6;
            color: #6B7280;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', monospace;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Boutons */
        .actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--adn-primary) 0%, var(--adn-primary-light) 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px -3px rgba(28, 41, 161, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px -5px rgba(28, 41, 161, 0.5);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            color: #64748B;
            border: 2px solid #E2E8F0;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #F8FAFC;
            border-color: #CBD5E1;
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--adn-primary);
            border: 2px solid var(--adn-primary);
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background: rgba(28, 41, 161, 0.05);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .header {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            .logo {
                height: 35px;
            }

            .error-card {
                padding: 1.5rem;
                border-radius: 1rem;
                margin: 0 0.5rem;
            }

            .error-icon {
                width: 64px;
                height: 64px;
            }

            .error-icon svg {
                width: 32px;
                height: 32px;
            }

            .error-title {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
            }

            .error-message-box p,
            .info-box p {
                font-size: 0.85rem;
            }

            .btn {
                padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
                font-size: 0.95rem;
            }
        }

        /* Particules */
        .particle {
            position: fixed;
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 50%;
            pointer-events: none;
            animation: float 15s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        .particle:nth-child(1) { left: 10%; top: 20%; animation-delay: 0s; }
        .particle:nth-child(2) { left: 20%; top: 60%; animation-delay: 2s; }
        .particle:nth-child(3) { left: 70%; top: 30%; animation-delay: 4s; }
        .particle:nth-child(4) { left: 80%; top: 70%; animation-delay: 6s; }
        .particle:nth-child(5) { left: 50%; top: 80%; animation-delay: 8s; }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); opacity: 0.3; }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px) translateX(10px); opacity: 0.6; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Particules -->
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>
    <div class="particle"></div>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header">
        <a href="{{ path('app_home') }}">
            <img src="{{ asset('build/theme/images/ADN_Logo_enlarged_x5.png') }}" alt="ADN Family Office" class="logo">
        </a>
    </header>

    <!-- Contenu principal -->
    <main class="main-container">
        <div class="error-card">
            <div class="error-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                    <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/>
                    <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <h1 class="error-title">Erreur de connexion MoneyPitch</h1>

            <div class="error-message-box">
                <p>{{ error_message }}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <div class="info-box-title">
                    💡 Compte pas encore activé ?
                </div>
                <p>
                    Si vous venez de vous inscrire, votre accès MoneyPitch doit d'abord être activé par notre équipe. 
                    Vous recevrez un email de MoneyPitch pour définir votre mot de passe une fois votre compte activé.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="error-code">
                ⚠️ Code erreur : {{ error_code }}
            </div>

            <div class="actions">
                <a href="{{ path('app_moneypitch_redirect') }}" class="btn btn-outline">
                    🔄 Réessayer la connexion
                </a>
                <a href="{{ path('app_logout') }}" class="btn btn-primary">
                    🚪 Se déconnecter
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <p>© {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} <a href="{{ path('app_home') }}">ADN Family Office</a> — Besoin d'aide ? <a href="mailto:contact@adnfamilyoffice.fr">Contactez-nous</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
